===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Rockchip]] RK3566 @1.8GHz :SoC: Quad-Core ARM (Cortex-A55); NPU: 0.8 TOPS *GPU: ''Mali-G52'' (OpenGL ES3.2, OpenCL 2.0) :VPU (with 4K VP9 and 4K 10-bit H265/H264 decoding) *Storage: 32GB (eMMC) Flash *Memory: 2GB (LPDDR4) SDRAM *Wi-Fi: [[Broadcom]] BCM43456 :802.11bgn+ac (1T1R), BT 5.0 *Network: 1x GbE port via connectors *Power Source: 5V via connectors
